Phi effect
	marquee

Gestalt pyschology
	shape or form
	perception is based on complete objects
	not independent parts

	Law of figure-ground


	Law of Pragnanz
		law of simplicity

	Law of proximity
		objects near each other belong together as group

	Law of similarity
		similar attributes belong as group
			color, shape, size, brightness

	Law of closure
		incomplete figures are perceived as whole

	Law of common fate
		objects moving together belong to group

	Law of continuity
		objects aligned along line or curve belong together
			perceive the smoothest path

	Law of symmetry
		perceive objects as figures over ground
		symmetric around a central axis


		